move1.name: Petal Dance
move1.description: The user attacks the target by scattering petals for two to three turns. The user then becomes confused.

move2.name: Solar Beam
move2.description: In this two-turn attack, the user gathers energy and blasts a bundled beam on the next turn.

move3.name: Moonblast
move3.description: Borrowing the power of the moon, the user attacks the target. This may also lower the target's Sp. Atk stat.

move4.name: Sludge Bomb
move4.description: The user strikes the target with a sludge bomb. It may also poison the target.
